SUMMARY:Themed Thursday: Ladies Night
DESCRIPTION:West End Social and DJ Elroy present Themed Thursdays\, happening every other Thursday in the heart of Downtown Durham \nTo begin the series\, we’re celebrating Women’s History Month with Ladies Night — a night dedicated to the women who gave us the hits! Come celebrate with live music\, drink specials\, and cross those fingers for good weather to enjoy our outdoor patio! \nSounds by Breyonna Beats – R&B| HipHip | Afrobeat | Pop| Reggae
