SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Celebrations at Ponysaurus Brewing Co.!
DESCRIPTION:There’s liquid gold at the end of this rainbow! 🌟🌈🍻 Mark your calendars & join us for St. Patrick’s Day shenanigans Friday\, March 13 to Tuesday\, March 17! We’ve got special sips & bites all weekend long ⬇️ \n🍀 “The Four Leaf Clover” Specialty Flight:\n• “Red Velvet” – Export Stout & Stem’s Hibiscus Cider\n• “Irish Coffee” – Counter Culture Coffee Baltic Porter with whipped cream & nutmeg\n• “Luck of the Irish” – Bright green cocktail made with pineapple juice\, peach schnapps\, Jameson\, & seltzer\n• Pour of Jameson Irish Whiskey\n🥃 Jameson Irish Whiskey\n🍻 Our Export Stout – a dry\, light stout just like they sip on in Ireland\n🥘 Irish beef stew with sour cream and chives\n🥔 Baked potatoes\, bacon\, sour cream and green onions
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/st-patricks-celebrations-at-ponysaurus-brewing-co/
LOCATION:Ponysaurus Brewing Co.\, 219 Hood Street\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Brewery,Food & Drink,Holiday,St. Patrick's Day,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
