SUMMARY:ANNE HEARTT GREGORY: HORIZONS
DESCRIPTION:5 Points Gallery announces the upcoming exhibit by Anne Heartt Gregory titled Horizons. These new works are vibrant renditions of abstract landscapes that imply moving to higher ground. Terrains shift from orange to blue making distant vistas appear within reach. What’s just over the horizon? You are invited to come discover for yourself. Join us for our Third Friday Reception on February 20 from 6–9pm to meet the artist and experience this new body of work. Enjoy the varied creations of our ten Triangle-based artists working in painting\, sculpture\, fused glass\, mixed media\, and finely crafted furniture. The exhibition runs from February 19 through March 14. Image: Anne Gregory\, Radiant\, acrylic\, 22 x 22 inches \nVisit 5 Points Gallery in person or online at https://5pointsgallery.com. All work from the exhibition is available for shipping or pickup. Gallery hours: Thursdays and Fridays 5–9pm\, Saturdays 1–9pm. Artists are available to talk about their work. For a private viewing\, contact us at info@5pointsgallery.com.
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/anne-heartt-gregory-horizons/2026-03-13/
LOCATION:5 Points Gallery\, 109 E Chapel Hill St\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art,Date Night,Exhibit,Third Friday
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Anne-Heartt-Gregory-Radiant-6.jpeg
