SUMMARY:Pi(e) Day at The Durham
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate 3.14 with us! Come to the Coffee Bar on Saturday\, March 14\, from 2pm until they are gone to enjoy pie on Pi(e) Day from acclaimed Durham baker\, Phoebe Lawless. We’ll have slices of Phoebe’s pies available for $3.14 at the Coffee Bar; pair your slice with lunch or an afternoon cup of Counter Culture Coffee. And now\, the moment you’ve been waiting for — we’ve confirmed Phoebe will be bringing these too good to miss flavors: Chocolate Chess\, Lemon Chess\, and Buttermilk Sugar. \nCome early and order weekend Brunch until 2pm\, or stick around and check out the afternoon Bar Menu if you need a little savory with your sweet.
