DESCRIPTION:Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo 2026\nJoin us for the Mind\, Body & Soul Wellness Expo\, a free\, family-friendly community event focused on mental health\, wellness\, and holistic healing. Hosted by NAMI Durham in partnership with Alliance Health and AmeriHealth Caritas North Carolina\, the expo brings together local organizations\, health professionals\, and community resources in one place. \nEnjoy live music\, line dancing\, mobile wellness screenings\, wellness vendors\, community resources\, and a fun Kids Zone with activities for the whole family. \n📍 Durham Central Park\n📅 Saturday\, March 14\, 2026\n⏰ 2:00 PM – 6:00 PM \nCome connect\, learn\, and take steps toward a healthier mind\, body\, and soul. 🌿
